<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span>طَلَاق بَائِن أَو رَجْعِيّ وَلم يُرَاجع أَو جن<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p58"></span>عقب ظِهَاره<a href="#p58" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p59"></span>فَلَا عود<a href="#p59" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>وَلَا كَفَّارَة فِي جَمِيع ذَلِك<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>وَكَذَا لَو<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>ظَاهر من زَوجته الرقيقة ثمَّ<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
